   -two difficulty levels (can be choosen from Options)
   -maximum amount of special function (build, clear, etc) can be set in Edit mode (doesn't affect game with Easy difficulty)
   -Push function

0.2.4
   -new command line switch: verbose - more messages
   -new command line switch: autonormal - automatically return to normal mode after using a function
   -new command line switch: noautoreload - when time is up, don't reload the level but end game
   -Options screen: you can set fullscreen, autoreload and autonormal values
   -error message if data directory not found
   -using configfile (data/config)
   -15 levels
   -level 13 is modified
   -in Highscore table level number is stored

